section_title: MATTERS RELATING TO PROTOCOL ARTICLE 2.3 (adverse impacts of policies and measures)
sentences: On this issue (FCCC/SB/2011/MISC.2), Eduardo Calvo Buendía (Peru) and Anastasia Theodorou (Hungary) will co-chair a joint SBI/SBSTA contact group on this item and Protocol Article 3.14 (adverse effects of response measures).
